 use?\n* Currently, OpenSpaces is in the early stages of development, but we plan to offer a range of pricing options to meet the needs of our users.\n5. How do I get started with OpenSpaces?\n* If you\'re interested in using OpenSpaces, you can sign up for our waiting list to be the first to know when we\'re ready to launch. We\'ll keep you updated on our progress and let you know as soon as we\'re ready to help you find your perfect space.\n\n\n--- Conversation 3 ---\nQuestion: rewrite this and include the fact that it\'s for those who wish to list property for leasing and teneats who wish to lease the property: \n\n" OpenSpaces is for anyone looking for commercial real estate and tenets, including small business owners, event planners, and commercial real estate property companies. "\nAnswer: Q: What makes OpenSpaces different from other commercial real estate platforms?\nA: OpenSpaces offers a unique combination of features, such as immediate access to a growing network of commercial real estate opportunities, a user-friendly platform that simplifies the process of finding the right space for your business, and a dedicated support team to assist you every step of the way. These features set OpenSpaces apart from other commercial real estate platforms and make it the go-to choice for businesses of all sizes.\n\n\n--- Conversation 4 ---\nQuestion: list of FAQ titles\nAnswer: "OpenSpaces is designed for both property owners looking to list their commercial real estate for leasing, and tenants searching for the perfect space to lease, including small business owners, event planners, and other commercial real estate seekers."\n\n\n--- Conversation 5 ---\nQuestion: Can I negotiate the lease directly through OpenSpaces?\nAnswer: 1. What is OpenSpaces?\n2. Who is OpenSpaces for?\n3. How does OpenSpaces work?\n4. What makes OpenSpaces different from other commercial real estate platforms?\n5. How can I list my property on OpenSpaces?\n6. How can I find the right space for my business on OpenSpaces?\n7. Is there a fee to use OpenSpaces?\n8. Can I negotiate the lease directly through OpenSpaces?\n9. How do I sign up for OpenSpaces?\n10. What support does OpenSpaces provide for its users? [/INST]', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=0, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=100, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None, extra_args=None), prompt_token_ids: None, prompt_embeds shape: None, lora_request: None, prompt_adapter_request: None.
